linuxwacom: linuxwacom (Wacom tablets drivers)
linuxwacom:
linuxwacom: The Linux Wacom Project manages the drivers, libraries, and 
linuxwacom: documentation for configuring and running Wacom tablets 
linuxwacom: under the Linux operating system. It contains diagnostic 
linuxwacom: applications as well as updated kernel drivers and 
linuxwacom: XFree86/Xorg XInput drivers.
linuxwacom:
linuxwacom: (See http://linuxwacom.sf.net/index.php/howto/inputdev et sqq.
linuxwacom:  for how to modify your Xorg configuration.)
